data.description: Welcome to a distinctive 2-story residence nestled in the heart of Fargo, ND, radiating unmatched character and potential. Perfectly set on a spacious corner lot, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home stands as a beacon of opportunity in Fargo's bustling real estate market. Inside, the ambiance of yesteryear is preserved, with a wood fireplace acting as the centerpiece, promising cozy evenings filled with warmth. Not just a regular parking space, the unique detached A-frame garage offers not only secure parking but also hosts an additional room above it, perfect for a studio, workshop, or added storage. While the home is steeped in vintage charm, it presents an exciting canvas for those looking to infuse their personal touch. Yes, it awaits some updating, but with a bit of modernization, it could quickly transform into a contemporary haven. Outside, the shady backyard beckons with promises of summer barbecues, relaxation, and maybe a garden of your own. Given its combination of charm, potential, and prime location, this listing is a rare gem in the real estate landscape. Don't miss out on this golden opportunity to make this house your dream home. Call today for your own private showing!
